cdata.name: Signals Network
cdata.desc: The Signals Network platform is a decentralized platform where users can create fully customizable trading robots with no advanced technical knowledge required. Based on the Ethereum network, the SGN token allows holders to create their own crypto-trading models based on premium indicators developed by data science community, perform complex machine learning experiments using super computer on historical data, or rent and copy-trade other successful strategies in Signals marketplace.
